.TH WEATHER 1 "March 2026" "weather-cli 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
weather \- terminal weather dashboard
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B weather
.SH DESCRIPTION
Weather is a terminal-based weather dashboard that provides
current conditions, hourly temperature graph, 7-day forecast,
moon phase, sunrise and sunset times.
.SH OPTIONS
Currently no command-line options.
